[h2] Why SomMark? [end]

[Block]
SomMark was born out of a desire for a structural markup language that maintains the readability of text while providing the power of a DSL. Unlike Markdown, which is primarily focused on rendering HTML, (SomMark is built for transformation)->(bold).
[end]

[Block]
Key benefits include:
[end]

[Block]
- (Structural Integrity)->(bold): Documents are inherently structured into blocks.
- (Named Props)->(bold): Easier management of complex components.
- (Native MDX Support)->(bold): Direct mapping to React/UI components.
[end]

